Brief instructions to install and run VisualClassification Library
-----------------------------------------------------

Author:Tarek Taha (tataha@cas.edu.au)
based on the EyePatch Windows Library http://hci.stanford.edu/research/eyepatch/

Sections:
---------

* Dependencies
* Compiling
* Using

Dependencies:
-------------

1) Opencv : 1.1pre or 2.1
2) Boost
3) Tesseract : (optional, necessary if you want to use text OCR) 
4) CMake

Compiling:
-------------
1) cd build
2) cmake ..
3) make

Using:
-------------
To be added later